title: Revo Uninstaller Pro 3.0.8 + Patch - XenoCoder
description:
Description:
Revo Uninstaller Pro is an easy-to-use yet very powerful program that will help you uninstall and remove unwanted programs installed on your computer even if you have problems uninstalling and cannot uninstall them from "Windows Add or Remove Programs" control panel applet. 

Revo Uninstaller Pro is a much faster and more powerful alternative to "Windows Add or Remove Programs" applet! It has very powerful features to uninstall and remove programs.

What's New in Version 3.08 (December 16th, 2013) :
Added - Backup creation before Traced Uninstall
Added Norwegian language and updated language files
Fixed bugs
